    <h1>What Is Diamox and Should You Take It on Kilimanjaro?</h1>
    <p>An honest guide to Diamox (acetazolamide) for Mount Kilimanjaro: how it works, who benefits, dosing, side effects, when it doesn't help, and what to discuss with your doctor.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span>By <a href="/about">Nelson Mushi</a></span>
      <span>&middot; 2026-06-14</span>
      <span>&middot; <a href="/blog">Back to Blog</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>
